About
City Walk is a design-inspired open-air lifestyle destination in Dubai that spans an area of more than 10 million square feet. Nestled in a prestigious neighbourhood on Al Safa Street in close proximity to the arterial Sheikh Zayed Road and the sophisticated Jumeirah Street, the family-friendly hub seamlessly combines living, retail, F&B, entertainment, hospitality and wellness options within one integrated space to offer visitors a unique sense of community and comfort. Designed to evolve as a city within a city, City Walk has emerged as the preferred choice for residents and tourists looking for a sophisticated place to shop, dine, socialize and spend quality time in a serene ambience in the heart of Dubai. City Walk is home to Canadian University Dubai and will soon have Talabat’s 150,000 sq ft HQ that will be split across two separate buildings, with the first set of employees expected to be moved in by Q3 2022.
Duration: More than 3 hours

Best walk ever !!
May 2023 • Friends
If you are a type of person that enjoys walking, well you are lucky you found this review ! Dubai City Walk is definitely one of my top places in Dubai , it is actually a very unique shaped concept which makes you feel like you are in the future ! I do not know if i should talk about the amazing luxury shops or about the wide selection of restaurants and cafes!

As known that Dubai is a city full of traffic, so they offer large parking spaces. The most coolest thing about Dubai City Walk in summer that the outdoor is cooled, you will stay cooled during summer high temperatures and enjoy your time ! It is crazy isn’t it ? In addition to the variety of arcade games in there for all ages.

In my humble opinion, It is totally a place that is worth to go at any time of the year ,you will have the perfect walking experience whether it is with your friends or family .However, it is a pretty small place, but if you got bored you can sit on the beach close to it and relax.

All in all, if you are looking for a perfect walk and you are sick of going to the same places ,well here is your chance , you better not miss this awesome this chance of visiting Dubai City Walk!
